Title: Good Luck, Have Fun
Description:
I've got some customers lined up that wanna collect some good old fashioned ears. But not any old ears. They only want the absolute waxiest ears money can buy! 

Guess they think they're lucky or something'.

Anyways, I need you to go get 'em for me. I don't want to hurt any animals, so you'll need to get 'em from the Alliance over at Lion's Landing.

Have fun - and remember, only bring me the waxiest!
ObjectivesText: Collect 10 Extra-Waxy Alliance Ears at Lion's Landing in Krasarang Wilds.
